text: We started @biotsCH at @ETH_en in 2016 to educate students on dApps We teach the CAS blockchain at @hslu with @GeorgesGrivas since 2017 We educated major law firms on blockchain & smart contracts in 2018 We target academic infrastructure with @seedvalidity & @ethliblab in 2019
